{
  "name": "RPlog_A_Dark_Secret",
  "title": "A Dark Secret",
  "summary": "At the rebuilt Sandbar in Plaxton City on Caspar, Jessalyn and her Jedi apprentice Orson are sharing a rare quiet drink when Jessalyn spots Bazil McKenzie, the bionic agent she once saved from electrocution on a beach. Orson confesses his own dark secret: months earlier he tortured Bazil in the woods at the base, an act he now regrets, tangled up in business between Bazil and Karrde. A badly drunk Bazil topples off his barstool, and when Orson goes to help, the disoriented agent mistakes him for multiple clones, kisses him on the cheek, and leers at Jessalyn before slurring his goodbyes. Throughout, Orson silently conveys his regret, anxiety, and gratitude through the Force, while Jessalyn reassures him they will talk later. Bazil slips out of the bar with unnatural, sober precision once outside, trailed by the curious patron Malus, leaving Orson resolved to set firm boundaries with his troublesome past acquaintance.",
